thread.title_full: Lucky Tackle Box reviewed by Dylan Hawkins

author: Dylan Hawkins
title: Dylan Hawkins
text: Love getting LTB it's the only thing I look forward to in the mail! Never had any issue! 100% satisfied! And the staff is great, they're always just a email away. Helping with any of your questions or needs! Andrew Schwartz helped me with many questions and was always there with a quick response! Great job guys! Only way it could get better is if I won that year free subscription! :)
